snippet: The Canadian government will ship 800 vials of its experimental Ebola vaccine to the World Health Organization in Geneva beginning on Monday, the Public Health Agency of Canada said on Saturday....

headline.print_headline: Canada to Ship Experimental Ebola Vaccine to WHO in Geneva
headline.main: Canada to Ship Experimental Ebola Vaccine to WHO in Geneva

lead_paragraph: The Canadian government will ship 800 vials of its experimental Ebola vaccine to the World Health Organization in Geneva beginning on Monday, the Public Health Agency of Canada said on Saturday.
